。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　3 　　月　　30　　日\r\n                                書記官　周芳安","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDV/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c678%2c20220330%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDV,111,訴,678,20220330,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"678","JDATE":"20220330","JTITLE":"清償借款"}